overview: Kubus Home Video presents a Kimberly Kubus film; the brand new in garbage cinema. The Pink Umbrella Man has a cabin possessed when Bob Booze and his friends are driving up. Meanwhile detectives mr. Dick and mr. Head put themselves on the task of solving the mystery. 31 minutes of bugs, guts, breeze, pizza, subways, hats and other stuff. Written & Directed by Kimberly, this movie even has its own theme song. A movie done in total Kubus style from top til bottom, it is rollercoaster cinema in stone delight.
tagline: the brand new in garbage cinema.
title: Complete Garbage
